"scene in a 3D environment. The viewer can also be frozen, so that the "
"visualization is not updated until you enter with the pointer in the work"
" area. When the preview mode is activated, it can display the rendered "
"animation as in the final render (see  :ref:`Previewing the Animation "
"<previewing_the_animation>`  )."
