" level formats specified into Preferences>Loading>Level Settings by "
"Format. In this case the Level Settings specified will be applied. It is "
"possible to add as many format as you want defining them by a Regular "
"Expression. This way, different settings can be automatically applied to "
"different kind of levels."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:66
msgid ""
