"browsers as a single animation level if they are named with a progressive"
" four-digits number written between the file name and the file extension,"
" e.g. ``animation.0001.tif`` , ``animation.0002.tif`` , etc. They are "
"displayed in the file browser with a double dot before the file "
"extension, e.g. ``animation..tif`` ."
msgstr ""

