"automatically to expose them in the xsheet or not, by setting the Expose "
"Loaded Levels in Xsheet option in the Preferences > Loading dialog. If "
"activated, each level will be placed in a different column, starting from"
" the first empty one. If deactivated, the loaded levels will be stored in"
