"greyed out in case a limited opacity is set."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:679
msgid ""
"A render toggle ( |Toonz71_246| ) allowing you to include or not the "
"column content in the rendering; when activated an eye icon is visible in"
" the toggle."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:681
msgid ""
"The camera stand and the render toggles are linked to similar toggles "
"available in the schematic column nodes (see  :ref:`Using the Stage "
"Schematic <using_the_stage_schematic>`  and  :ref:`Using the FX Schematic"
" <using_the_fx_schematic>`  )."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:683
msgid ""
"A lock toggle ( |Toonz71_247| ) allowing you to prevent any editing in "
"the column; when activated a padlock icon is visible in the toggle."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:687
msgid ""
"An area where the name of the column is displayed, that by default is the"
" name of the first exposed level. The area color indicates the type of "
"level exposed in the column."
