#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:867
msgid ""
"Use the Random command to rearrange the selected cells in a random order."
" The order changes every time you use the command."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/working_in_xsheet.rst:869
msgid ""
"Use the Autoexpose command to repeat the selected cells as if filling the"
" numbering gap between two subsequent drawings. For example if the "
"command is applied to two cells where drawing 2 and 5 are exposed, the "
"result will be four cells with drawings 2, 2, 2 and 5. The command works "
"only if the selection is increasingly numbered."
